Description:
Huge stamp duty savings!
If you purchase this brand new magnificent north facing apartment you will be surrounded by the peacefulness of nature. Lush plant life cascades around the building exterior, a rooftop garden provides fantastic views and moments of tranquillity. Balconies with planters offer private gardens..
The apartment layout provides flexible living options. Unique loft apartment is bright and airy with expansive windows and 4.5 metre high ceilings, residents can use their imagination and transform the additional mezzanine area into anything from a studio to a hobby room, kids' play area or guest retreat.
Resident facilities within the building include, private meeting rooms, swimming pool, spa & sauna, gym.
A short stroll or walk to Harbour town shopping centre, restaurants and cafes on the waterfront, a short tram ride into Melbourne CBD and the iconic Melbourne star wheel.
The apartment features
• 2 bedrooms with BIR's plus a great size loft area which can easily be converted to a 3rd bedroom
• Internal area: 101.5m2
• Balcony area: 11.5m2H• Total area: 113m2
• One car park space
Call today for any additional information you may require - Be quick!

Description:
Super-Sized Luxury Reveals Stunning Blue-Water Brilliance
Maximising natural northern light and blue-water views at every turn, this super-stylish 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom and 2 car parks with spacious storage cage apartment positively shimmers and shines in one of Melbourne's most requested city-edge locations. Simply stroll to the CBD, Southern Cross Station, Crown Entertainment Complex, and the restaurants and bars of New Quay with free city trams on your doorstep.
Move straight in and apply your personal touch with so much on offer. Discover the wide-reaching, north-facing comforts of open-plan living and dining on sleek timber flooring, complemented by a stone-topped kitchen with sparkling, stainless-steel appliances and an imposing breakfast bar. The stunning views are all-encompassing, overlooking Marvel Stadium, Victoria Harbour and sweeping across the horizon as far as the eye can see. Both window-walled bedrooms spectacularly share in these same memorable views, serviced by mirrored robes and a pair of extra-large, fully tiled bathrooms with the ensuite featuring a twin vanity.
Prominently positioned on the 29th floor of the tightly held Victoria Point tower, enjoy parking for two, a concealed laundry with a Fisher and Paykel dryer, ducted heating and cooling, roller blinds, openable windows, express lift, and video intercom entry. The building has it all including an on-site building manager, concierge and a professionally managed fitness centre.

Description:
Stunning 26th level Quays living with dazzling harbour views
From the remarkable views of Victoria Harbour to the bold modern luxury and outstanding quality that all buyers are constantly searching for, this exceptional two bedroom, two bathroom apartment is a 26th floor contemporary haven in the Docklands.
A fantastic balcony has views to the south and west, with Docklands Stadium and the calm waters of the harbour in full view. The immaculate interiors of this residence are truly special, from the lavish stone kitchen with colourful glass splashback and stainless steel Miele appliances, to the generous central living and meals zone with timber floors and full sliding doors out to the balcony.
Retire to the splendid master bedroom at the end of your long and tiring day, with this sizeable retreat promising built-in robe storage and a beautiful ensuite. You also can enjoy a 2nd bedroom with BIR, impressive main bathroom with concealed laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, massive storage cage and secure car space.
The state of the art Quays facilities are some of the best in the Docklands and include a Health Club with a pool, spa, sauna, gym and yoga studio, Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, and a rooftop garden with BBQ facilities and Docklands only Tennis Court.
This NewQuay Precinct location has you so close to fabulous restaurants and eateries including Capri Café and Lounge, Cargo, Mama Rumaan and Woolshed. You’re also positioned near the popular The District Docklands, Docklands Stadium for footy lovers, and trams on Docklands Drive and Harbour Esplanade transporting you across Melbourne.
To arrange an exclusive viewing please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304.

Description:
Resort style living in Marina Tower
Delivering on all residential fronts from the impeccable modern style to a position in the exclusive Marina Tower which offers standout facilities, this two bedroom apartment is only for serious buyers in search of the ultimate NewQuay Precinct residence.
An entry opens directly into the state of the art kitchen which promises sleek tiles underfoot, stone surfaces, elegant cabinetry, and stainless steel Miele appliances. A few steps on and you’ll find yourself in the relaxed lounge and dining room, which accesses the enclosed undercover alfresco area which is west-facing and suited for outdoor dinners and drinks.
Both bedrooms boast mirrored built-in robes, meanwhile the central bathroom has all the sleek trimmings and great mirrored cabinetry. Further embrace a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to a lobby lounge, library, business centre, meeting rooms, cinema, lounge and billiard room, kitchen and dining area, rooftop pool, gym, and expansive deck.
Metres to The District Docklands with restaurants and entertainment, eateries including Almina and Waterfront Fish Market Restaurant, Marvel Stadium, IGA supermarket, Ron Barassi Snr Park, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, and trams taking you across Melbourne.
Please contact Vicky Leong on 0452 486 860 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
Exclusive Concavo Waterfront Marina Home Available
The rarest of opportunity exists at this in-demand 5 Stars address that's is the 'Concavo'.
On offer is an as-new luxury Marina front three bedroom, two bathroom apartment perfectly elevated on the 1st floor. Directly facing North into the harbour to soak up all the serenity and the glittering water views.
This prestigious 'Concavo' building has set the bench-mark for all future living within the Docklands precinct. The 'never to be built out' views from this beautiful home could not be better as you peer from your living room or your spacious balcony directly onto the harbour front.
This breathtaking apartment comes with all the luxurious upgrades associated with the Marina Homes and comprises of three spacious bedrooms - Master with double vanity & bathtub ensuite, separate laundry room, a designer kitchen with top end stainless steel appliances, stone bench tops and an abundance of cupboard space, living room with amazing water views, a ultra wide balcony perfect for entertaining, ducted air conditioning/heating and two secure undercover car spaces plus storage cage.
Features: 24 hour concierge, residents lounge, business centre and board room, indoor cinema, north facing sky garden facing the water with BBQ facilities. 25 metres indoor heated pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and treatment room.
Don't miss your opportunity to secure this extremely rare Marina Home right by the waterside.
Please call Peter Doan on 0402 959 842 for more information.

Description:
Sumptuous Docklands living with beautiful water views
Absolutely flawless from head to toe thanks to the finest of fittings and finishes, this immaculate and superbly luxurious two bedroom apartment is your next Docklands residence situated in the Silver Tower of the brilliant Aqui Promenade complex.
You’ll feel right at the home the second you step inside this 8th floor oasis. Beautiful timber floors line the open plan lounge and dining zone, which has sliding door access out to a charming undercover balcony with picturesque water views where alfresco dinners and weekend drinks will be a must!
The stylish stone kitchen has everything you need including stainless steel Miele appliances, meanwhile both the bedrooms boast mirrored built-in robe storage and sit right near the deluxe bathroom which showcases chic black tapware, beautiful floor-to-ceiling tiles, and a rain shower. There is also a small private balcony off one of the bedrooms for added outdoor flexibility.
Other property highlights include a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom, secure car space, and access to an indoor 25m swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, and lobby with private meeting rooms.
Love the location opposite The District Docklands which has an array of great dining and entertainment options, while you’re also close to promenade restaurants, IGA X-Press supermarket, Etihad Stadium, and trams taking you across Melbourne.

Inner City Sophistication, Resort-Style Luxury
Showcasing an alluring blend of harbour side serenity, cosmopolitan convenience and resort-style luxury commensurate with the top 5-star hotels, this 1-bedroom apartment offers inner city living that is nothing short of spectacular. Streamlined, spacious and light-filled interiors are complemented by an extensive open-sky backdrop, while proximity to waterfront cafes & restaurants, Etihad Stadium sporting events and free public transport in and out of the neighbouring CBD make for a fantastic lifestyle. Within an elegant designer building where your recreation and relaxation know no bounds, you will love returning home to unwind in the spa, gym, tennis court, pool, yoga centre and private cinema or entertain in the rooftop gardens complete with BBQ and dining facilities.

Internal Size: 60sqm (approx.) excluding balcony
Rental Return: $460/wk currently on a month to month basis
Body Corporate Fees: $1,036.50/qtr
Council Rates: $1,071/annum

Description:
Snap Up This Dazzling and Designer Docklands Abode
Sitting on the banks of the picturesque Victoria Harbour and delivering breathtaking water views matched by an elegance and sophistication you’ll never get tired of, this ultra-contemporary two bedroom, two bathroom apartment in the coveted Conder complex is Docklands perfection.
This sensational building has a design by acclaimed Fender Katsalidis and sits ideally in the exclusive NewQuay precinct. You’ll have easy access to District Docklands Shopping Centre, Medibank Icehouse, Costco, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, and the handy 70, 86 & city circle tram which takes you through the CBD and all the way to the eastern suburbs. You’ll also have restaurants nearby including The Conder restaurant, NewQuay International Buffet, and Waterside Oriental Bistro.
This pristine 6th floor apartment is flawless in its presentation, boasting wonderful full height windows allowing for superb light, sleek roller blinds, quality carpet, and premium tapware. The open plan living and dining space easily opens out to a charmed balcony which has direct harbour views, meanwhile both bedrooms also share the superb vistas including the master haven which offers a study nook, walk-in robe, and private ensuite. The master bedroom also has direct balcony access.
The gourmet kitchen features stone benchtops and Miele appliances, the central bathroom is well-appointed, and other apartment extras include a European laundry, central heating and cooling, video intercom entry, storage cage, one secure car spaces, and access to Conder facilities including a pool, gym, and outdoor recreation area. This is a Docklands opportunity you need to seize!
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Complementing these features is split system heating & cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry, as well as use of the heated outdoor pool and gym.
If you are an astute investor, don’t miss out on this incredible chance to buy in the Docklands.

Description:
As Good As Gold
With so many plus points, this residential complex has the most divine harbour lifestyle offered.
Victoria Point, with it’s eye catching gold glass façade, is held in high regard in Docklands.
This fantastic 2 bedroom apartment, located on the 16th floor of the striking residential complex captures the most amazing views of the city skyline especially at night with offset views to the marina and Port Phillip Bay.
The apartment features a hostess designer kitchen with stainless steel appliances including gas stove top, stone benchtops and ample cupboard space. A dining area adjoins the open plan living room and a “Juliet” balcony.
The large main bedroom and 2nd bedroom, both with mirrored robes, shares the stylish contemporary bathroom. Other features include separate laundry, one secure undercover car space, storage cage, ducted air conditioning and heating.
Other features include
• Concierge and onsite manager
• Gymnasium
• Security entrance
Being in the heart of the Docklands, going to and from the apartment is a breeze.
Free tram zoned, close to Southern Cross station and with easy access to the freeway network.
Marvel at Etihad Stadium, restaurants and cafes in and around the area for you to enjoy.
Ready to move in now or perfect as an investment.

Description:
Wake up to Yarra views
Offering Panoramic views over the Yarra River, Victoria Harbour and the CBD, how could you resist this stunning one bedroom apartment at Yarra's Edge. During the day this wonderful apartment is bathed in natural sunlight and by night you will be mesmerized by the magnificent CBD backdrop.
The full sized open living area will suit the entertainer in you and if you love to cook, the fully renovated gourmet kitchen includes a symphony of quality appliances, stone bench top finishes, and integrated fridge / freezer. The main bedroom overlooks the Marina below and offers built in robes and balcony access. The facilities include access to Mirvac’s Rekdek which includes indoor heated lap pool, spa, steam and sauna room, and fully equipped gymnasium.
located in the superb and highly sought-after Yarra’s Edge precinct featuring some of Melbourne best restaurants and bars down on South Wharf including The General Assembly, The Boatbuilders Yard, Munich Brauhaus and just a stones throw away from Crown Casino, Victoria Harbour precinct, DFO South Wharf, Southern Cross Station, and trams on Spencer Street and Flinders Street.
For inspection call Glenn Donnelly on 0419 998 235.

Description:
A luxury modern statement in Yarra’s Edge
An array of stunning highlights awaits one lucky buyer on the 25th floor of this luxury Docklands building, with this 2 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom residence promising a level of quality that is second to none plus astonishing CBD and water views that you will never get tired of.
The ‘Array’ complex in the Yarra’s Edge precinct is the setting for this contemporary haven. The exceptional views of the marina below and CBD buildings in the distance will be the first thing you notice, with the large covered balcony the ideal vantage point for the views as you sit back with a wine and enjoy the warm summer breeze.
The central living zone consists of areas to lounge and dine, with the adjoining kitchen equipped with stone surfaces, the convenience of an island bench, and stainless steel Miele appliances. The master retreat has a large built-in robe and chic dual vanity ensuite, meanwhile also be impressed by the sizeable 2nd bedroom, a study room or potential 3rd bedroom, main bathroom, separate laundry/ storage room, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces.
Enjoy exclusive access to on-site gym & residence lounge, plus the fantastic RekDek facilities which include a gym, pool, spa, steam room, and sauna. You’re near DFO Shopping and South Wharf Promenade which enjoys terrific bars and eateries including The General Assembly, Plus 5 Bar, Meat Market, and The Boatbuilders Yard, Crown Entertainment Complex with world class restaurants, Melbourne’s lively CBD, trams, and Southern Cross Station.
